01:25:57.828 --> 01:25:59.568
<i>The media blackout
was finally lifted...</i>

01:25:59.663 --> 01:26:01.574
<i>with a press conference
early this morning.</i>

01:26:01.665 --> 01:26:04.122
<i>I'm feeling privileged,</i>

01:26:04.209 --> 01:26:06.370
<i>and,</i>

01:26:06.461 --> 01:26:08.417
<i>oddly, I'm proud.</i>

01:26:10.340 --> 01:26:13.377
<i>And, of course,
nervous and excited.</i>

